ComicInfo.Title: The Maddening Menace of the Super-Beast!; The Fiery Breath of Fafnir!
ComicInfo.Summary:
The Maddening Menace of the Super-Beast!: Thor and the New Men defeat the Man-Beast. The High Evolutionary takes the spaceship part of Wundagore to the stars.
The Fiery Breath of Fafnir!: Thor and companions fight Fafnir to find Volstagg.
